'''2016年环西自行车赛'''是第71届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2016年8月20日至9月11日进行，此次比赛是2016年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.velonews.com/events/vuelta-a-espana/2016-vuelta-route-harder-than-last-years/|title=2016 Vuelta route harder than last year's?|work=VeloNews|date=2016-01-07|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929122718/https://www.velonews.com/events/vuelta-a-espana/2016-vuelta-route-harder-than-last-years/|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[森列|森列]]，终点位于[[马德里|马德里]]<ref name=cn-route-announced>{{cite news|title=Vuelta a Espana 2016 race route revealed|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-2016-race-route-revealed/|accessdate=2016-01-09|work=Cyclingnews.com|date=2016-01-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517142752/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-2016-race-route-revealed/|archivedate=2016-05-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中18支车队为世界职业车队，另外4支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref name=cw-wildcards>{{cite news|title=Vuelta a Espana 2016 teams announced|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-2016-teams-announced/|accessdate=2016-08-21|work=Cyclingnews.com|date=2016-05-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507050540/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-2016-teams-announced/|archivedate=2016-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自移动之星车队的哥伦比亚车手[[奈洛·金塔纳|奈洛·金塔纳]]获得此次比赛的总冠军，成为史上第二位获得环西自行车赛总冠军的哥伦比亚选手<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rtve.es/deportes/20160911/madrid-vive-fiesta-colombiana-honor-vuelta-nairo-quintana/1398063.shtml|script-title=es:Madrid vive una fiesta colombiana en honor a la Vuelta de Nairo Quintana|publisher=rtve|date=2016-09-11|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914010544/http://www.rtve.es/deportes/20160911/madrid-vive-fiesta-colombiana-honor-vuelta-nairo-quintana/1398063.shtml|archivedate=2016-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自天空车队的[[克里斯·弗鲁姆|克里斯·弗鲁姆]]以1分23秒之差获得第二名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/15264/10574823/vuelta-a-espana-chris-froome-says-2016-has-been-his-best-year-yet|title=Vuelta a Espana: Chris Froome says 2016 has been his best year yet|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2016-09-12|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929123537/https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/15264/10574823/vuelta-a-espana-chris-froome-says-2016-has-been-his-best-year-yet|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>。金塔纳的同胞，来自Orica–BikeExchange车队的[[Esteban_Chaves|Esteban Chaves]]则获得第三名<ref>{{cite web|url=https://colombia.as.com/colombia/2016/09/11/masdeporte/1473614780_886721.html|script-title=es:Así fue el 2016 de Chaves, tercero en la Vuelta a España|publisher=AS|date=2016-09-11|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929123347/https://colombia.as.com/colombia/2016/09/11/masdeporte/1473614780_886721.html|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>。

